## 🧪 **테스트 결과**

### **API 테스트**
```bash
# 헬스체크
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/extract-social-metadata
# 결과: {"status":"healthy","service":"social-metadata-extractor",...}

# Instagram 추출 테스트
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/extract-social-metadata \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/example", "platform": "instagram"}'
# 결과: {"success":true,"message":"instagram 메타데이터 추출 완료",...}
```

